How to send sms to user when registered.

1. upload the plugin to wordpress site.
2. A submenu will appears DSP_Admin > Twilio
3. Register a twilio account, with your username and password
4. On Twilio account page, it will ask to get a new test phone number.
5. On Twilio accout page, there is a section Phone numbers > Verified caller ID. Verify your own number for test purpose.
5. After getting the number, you will get the SID and AUTH TOKEN, which you should copy and save it in DSP_ADMIN > Twilio page.
6. For auto login process add the dsp_add_ons add_on.